summary: 1999  was a common year starting on Friday of the Gregorian calendar.
full_text: Sultan Salahuddin Abdul Aziz Shah Al-Haj Ibni Al-Marhum Sultan Hisamuddin Alam Shah Al-Haj  was the eleventh Yang di-Pertuan Agong of Malaysia and eighth Sultan of Selangor.
title: Sultan Salahuddin Abdul Aziz Shah ibni Almarhum Sultan Hisamuddin Alam Shah Al-Haj
